    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Visual works made of plaster, which is a soft, plastic material, in this context usually a mixture of water, lime, and sand, often combined with other materials, such as animal hair. Plasterworks are either applied smoothly to a surface or as a combination of high-relief, sculptural, and surface decoration.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
